FaveCon AddressBook Installation Instructions
=============================================


Requirements
------------
 * Apache Webserver
 * PHP version 5.2 or greater including MySQL-Support
 * MySQL database engine
 * MySQL InnoDB support for recovery feature
 * The permission to create databases and tables in the MySQL database engine
 * PHP cURL support for: Facebook Integration, Update notification for System users
 * API keys for Facebook and/or Google Maps if you want to use these features


Installation
------------
 1. Decompress the archive and put this folder somewhere inside your document root
 2. Add your database config to config/config.db.php
 3. Create the MySQL database
 4. Point your browser to http://url-to-FaveCon/installer/
 5. Follow the instruction of the install script
 6. Remove the install directory
 7. Done!


UPDATE
